  "detailed_description": "Rise Of  Three Kingdoms is a Three Kingdoms history simulation strategy game. To make the product more realistic, we have browsed Records of the Three Kingdoms, Book of Later Han, ZiZhiTongJian and The spring and Autumn period of Emperor Xian. We also sort out material with eight hundred thousand words as the reference resources for the game design. During the period of study the details of Three Kingdoms, we have found many interesting facts. For example, Liubei was actually a man with nor beard; Jianggan, who stole the books was a handsome guy; the mother of Zhanglu had secret relationship with Liuzhang's father, who was the enemy of the former one... As we designed the game, we tried to put as much details as possible into the game and provide you a more realistic Three Kingdoms world.<br>As a lord of a certain territory, you will appoint your interior officers to search and visit the celebrities and input them to the generals list of Three Kingdoms. You can use different arrays and the advantages of the terrain against enemies with more soldiers than you. Military and strategical movement will be launched on the map. Welcome to prosper the Han Dynasty!<br><br><br><u>The game is in the stage of preemptive experience, and we will continually fix bugs and optimize the details. We will also add up many new contents and game plays, which will be updated on Steam. If you have any problem during the period of your playing, or if you have any suggestion and opinion, please tell us . We will provide you with better game experience and fun!</u><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270980/extras/7c49bde6e659f39114d73774e0d429e8.poster.avif?t=1734687925\" width=120 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270980/extras/7c49bde6e659f39114d73774e0d429e8.webm?t=1734687925\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>     <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270980/extras/62d9173d3c6c22b6c7927d3ebdd6375f.poster.avif?t=1734687925\" width=120 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270980/extras/62d9173d3c6c22b6c7927d3ebdd6375f.webm?t=1734687925\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span> <br><strong>game features</strong><br>More than 600 generals will appear and all the character design is restored accroding to the Three Kingdom history. The real Three Kingdoms culture will be magnified. (for instance:)<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270980/extras/7c49bde6e659f39114d73774e0d429e8.poster.avif?t=1734687925\" width=120 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270980/extras/7c49bde6e659f39114d73774e0d429e8.webm?t=1734687925\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>     <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270980/extras/62d9173d3c6c22b6c7927d3ebdd6375f.poster.avif?t=1734687925\" width=120 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270980/extras/62d9173d3c6c22b6c7927d3ebdd6375f.webm?t=1734687925\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span> <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270980/extras/daff738239be70ff08056f75a758e5bd.post