57d45b3f8233d0c868e4f7a86ede458e.mp4?t=1734687925\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270980/extras/a3c874ac697bc83313c5e6b16646ae66.poster.avif?t=1734687925\" width=400 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270980/extras/a3c874ac697bc83313c5e6b16646ae66.webm?t=1734687925\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270980/extras/a3c874ac697bc83313c5e6b16646ae66.mp4?t=1734687925\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Political and military strategical game which is easy for beginners to play.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270980/extras/a3c874ac697bc83313c5e6b16646ae66.poster.avif?t=1734687925\" width=400 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270980/extras/a3c874ac697bc83313c5e6b16646ae66.webm?t=1734687925\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270980/extras/a3c874ac697bc83313c5e6b16646ae66.mp4?t=1734687925\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270980/extras/26cb9094221b58757e8d14e8b48a678c.poster.avif?t=1734687925\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270980/extras/26cb9094221b58757e8d14e8b48a678c.webm?t=1734687925\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270980/extras/26cb9094221b58757e8d14e8b48a678c.mp