se from different monarchs to have various experience. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270980/extras/a80cced9e6fb8c93adfa51db5d2b0775.poster.avif?t=1734687925\" width=476 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270980/extras/a80cced9e6fb8c93adfa51db5d2b0775.webm?t=1734687925\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270980/extras/a80cced9e6fb8c93adfa51db5d2b0775.mp4?t=1734687925\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Rise Of  Three Kingdoms is for the players below:<br>Who like playing Three Kingdoms series games<br>Who like simulation or strategical game<br>Who are interested in history especially the history of Three Kingdoms period<br>Who have independent thinking habit in strategical battle<br>Who collect and cultivate Three Kingdoms characters<br>Who like develop the cities of his own.",
